The paper is about a research framework for deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the implementation of deep RL agents, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of deep RL in robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY), which are relevant subfields. Finally, the paper briefly mentions the use of deep RL in computer vision (cs.CV), although this is not the main focus of the paper.
